description:
The status of the document in the process. Possible values are:
- RECE (Received)
- DRFT (Drafted)
- PENA (Pending Approval)
- PENU (Pending Update)
- PENC (Pending Confirmation)
- CONF (Confirmed)
- REJE (Rejected)
- APPR (Approved)
- ISSU (Issued)
- SURR (Surrendered)
- SUBM (Submitted)
- VOID (Void)
- CANC (Cancelled)
- CMPL (Completed)
